<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>앙상블 스타즈 캐릭터 매칭 테스트</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
}

:root{
    --main:#4f46e5;
    --pink:#ec4899;
}

body{
    font-family:'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
    min-height:100vh;
    background:linear-gradient(135deg,#eef2ff,#ffe4f3);
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:center;
    padding:20px;
}

.quiz-wrap{
    width:100%;
    max-width:700px;
}

.card{
    background:white;
    border-radius:24px;
    padding:40px;
    box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
}

.title{
    text-align:center;
    margin-bottom:30px;
}

.title h1{
    font-size:2rem;
    color:var(--main);
}

.title p{
    margin-top:10px;
    color:#666;
}

.progress-wrap{
    margin-bottom:25px;
}

.progress-text{
    display:flex;
    justify-content:space-between;
    margin-bottom:8px;
    font-size:14px;
    color:#666;
}

.progress-bar{
    height:10px;
    background:#ddd;
    border-radius:999px;
    overflow:hidden;
}

.progress{
    height:100%;
    width:0%;
    background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--main),var(--pink));
    transition:0.3s;
}

.badge{
    display:inline-block;
    background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--main),var(--pink));
    color:white;
    padding:6px 14px;
    border-radius:999px;
    font-size:13px;
    font-weight:700;
    margin-bottom:20px;
}

.question{
    font-size:1.2rem;
    font-weight:700;
    line-height:1.6;
    margin-bottom:30px;
}

.choices{
    display:flex;
    flex-direction:column;
    gap:14px;
}

.choice-btn{
    width:100%;
    border:none;
    border-radius:16px;
    padding:18px;
    text-align:left;
    background:#f8fafc;
    border:2px solid #e2e8f0;
    cursor:pointer;
    transition:0.2s;
    display:flex;
    gap:14px;
    align-items:flex-start;
}

.choice-btn:hover{
    transform:translateY(-2px);
    border-color:var(--main);
    background:#eef2ff;
}

.choice-btn.selected{
    border-color:var(--main);
    background:linear-gradient(135deg,#eef2ff,#ffe4f3);
}

.choice-key{
    width:34px;
    height:34px;
    border-radius:50%;
    background:#cbd5e1;
    color:#334155;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:center;
    font-weight:700;
    flex-shrink:0;
}

.choice-btn.selected .choice-key{
    background:var(--main);
    color:white;
}

.choice-text{
    line-height:1.5;
    font-weight:600;
    color:#334155;
}

.nav{
    margin-top:30px;
    display:flex;
    gap:12px;
}

.btn{
    border:none;
    border-radius:999px;
    padding:14px 22px;
    cursor:pointer;
    font-weight:700;
    transition:0.2s;
}

.back{
    background:white;
    border:2px solid #cbd5e1;
}

.next{
    flex:1;
    background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--main),var(--pink));
    color:white;
    opacity:0.4;
    pointer-events:none;
}

.next.active{
    opacity:1;
    pointer-events:auto;
}

.next.active:hover{
    transform:translateY(-2px);
}

@media(max-width:600px){
    .card{
        padding:25px;
    }

    .question{
        font-size:1rem;
    }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="quiz-wrap">
    <div class="card">

        <div class="title">
            <h1>✨ MY DESTINY PARTNER ✨</h1>
            <p>나와 가장 잘 어울리는 앙스타 캐릭터는?</p>
        </div>

        <div class="progress-wrap">
            <div class="progress-text">
                <span id="progressLabel">1 / 20</span>
                <span id="categoryLabel">열정</span>
            </div>

            <div class="progress-bar">
                <div class="progress" id="progress"></div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="badge" id="badge">열정</div>

        <div class="question" id="question"></div>

        <div class="choices" id="choices"></div>

        <div class="nav">
            <button class="btn back" onclick="prevQuestion()">← 이전</button>
            <button class="btn next" id="nextBtn" onclick="nextQuestion()">다음 →</button>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>

<form id="hiddenForm" action="/match" method="POST" style="display:none"></form>

